<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.1">
<l>aiya puḻutiyuṭam paḷaintivaḷ pēccu malantalaiyāy</l>
<l>ceyyanūliṉ ciṟṟāṭai ceppaṉu ṭukkavum vallaḷallaḷ</l>
<l>kaiyiṉil ciṟutūtai yōṭivaḷ muṟṟil pirintumilaḷ</l>
<l>paiyarava ṇaippaḷḷi yāṉō ṭukaivait tivaḷvarumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lord! Her body covered in dust, [her] speech vexed,</l>
<l>She is not able to cover [her] hips</l>
<l rend="indent">with the the small garment [made] of red thread!</l>
<l>She cannot even part from the winnow and</l>
<l rend="indent">little toy utensils in [her] hands!</l>
<l>[Yet here] she comes [her] hand-in-hand</l>
<l rend="indent">with him who sleeps on the hooded serpent bed!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
